message:
Running command: cd /workspace/SheepVibes && git commit -m "feat: make each widget's feed URL editable

- Implement backend PUT endpoint /api/feeds/<feed_id> for updating feed URLs
- Add frontend edit button (✎) to each feed widget
- Create modal dialog for editing feed URLs with validation
- Add CSS styling for edit button and modal
- Implement JavaScript functionality for edit workflow
- Fix backend import issues and function naming conflicts
- Configure CORS for frontend-backend communication
- Update documentation (TODO.md, CHANGELOG.md)
- All backend tests passing (74/74, 1 skipped)

Co-authored-by: openhands <openhands@all-hands.dev>"
